ygData.subject: RE: [EQ_Necromancer] Collecting Bone Chips
ygData.msgSnippet: I think the Paineel Newbie zone is probably the highest concentration of skeletons in the game.  They spawn 5 at a time and I don t think I ve ever had to wait
ygData.messageBody:
I think the Paineel Newbie zone is probably the highest concentration of
skeletons in the game. They spawn 5 at a time and I don't think I've ever
had to wait for a target. I had 160 chips in the bank before I reached
level 3.

Alazzar
Mith Marr Server

-----Original Message-----
From: Aazen1@... [mailto:Aazen1@...]
Sent: Sunday, April 09, 2000 5:38 PM
To: EQ_Necromancer@onelist.com
Subject: [EQ_Necromancer] Collecting Bone Chips


I have a question that I think will benefit every single person on this
list.
As you all know, once our supply of bone chips runs low, we then often times

have to spend a large amount of platinum buying a fresh supply from younger
players or spend several hours gathering them ourselves. In the hopes of
making this burden easier on all of us, I come asking : Where do you go to
collect your chips? I ask that anyone who knows of a good place to go when
seeking bone chips shares it with this list. Any and all replies are
appreciated.

Walk in Darkness,
Aazen Sy'Vex
